{"id": "art-582", "label": "Art. 582", "title": "Art. 582: Revocarea sau anularea amânării aplicării pedepsei", "slug": "art-582", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1493902316\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1124\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1493902316\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 582:\nRevocarea sau anularea amân&#259;rii aplic&#259;rii pedepsei </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1107466543\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1123\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1107466543\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Asupra revoc&#259;rii sau anul&#259;rii amân&#259;rii\naplic&#259;rii pedepsei se pronun&#355;&#259;, din oficiu sau la sesizarea\nprocurorului sau a consilierului de proba&#355;iune, instan&#355;a care\njudec&#259; ori a judecat în prim&#259; instan&#355;&#259; infrac&#355;iunea ce\nar putea atrage revocarea sau anularea.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1440860485\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1122\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1440860485\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Dac&#259; pân&#259; la expirarea termenului\nprev&#259;zut la art. 86 alin. (4) lit. c) din Codul penal persoana cu privire\nla care s-a dispus amânarea aplic&#259;rii pedepsei nu a respectat\nobliga&#355;iile civile stabilite prin hot&#259;rârea prin care s-a dispus\namânarea, serviciul de proba&#355;iune competent sesizeaz&#259; instan&#355;a\ncare a pronun&#355;at în prim&#259; instan&#355;&#259; amânarea, în vederea\nrevoc&#259;rii acesteia. Sesizarea poate fi f&#259;cut&#259; &#351;i de\nprocuror sau de partea interesat&#259;, pân&#259; la expirarea termenului de\nsupraveghere.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_941261200\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1121\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_941261200\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Dac&#259; constat&#259; c&#259; sunt îndeplinite\ncondi&#355;iile art. 88 sau 89 din Codul penal, instan&#355;a, anulând sau,\ndup&#259; caz, revocând amânarea aplic&#259;rii pedepsei, dispune condamnarea\ninculpatului &#351;i executarea pedepsei stabilite prin hot&#259;rârea de\namânare, aplicând apoi, dup&#259; caz, dispozi&#355;iile cu privire la\nconcursul de infrac&#355;iuni, recidiv&#259; sau pluralitate intermediar&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;text-align:center'><span style='mso-no-proof:\nyes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape id=\"Imagine_x0020_1119519149\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1120\"\n type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;\n mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1119519149\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>SEC&#354;IUNEA 1<sup>1</sup>:Schimb&#259;ri\nîn executarea unor hot&#259;râri</span></b></p>"}